title: Batman - Unseen 01-05 (2009-2010|Digital|Minutemen-PhD)
description:
Promotional info for the collected edition - "The fan-favorite Bat-team of Doug Moench and Kelley Jones reunite to introduce the newest member of Batman's rogues gallery in this 5-issue miniseries! Horrible and unexplained murders have Gotham City held captive. Bizarre deaths have been occurring throughout the city, but the perpetrator is unknown. Even when the crimes have been committed in view of witnesses, all that is seen is a glimpse of a weird, skinless man who seems to fade away after the crimes. Gotham's only hope is their Dark Knight Detective, but how can Batman find and fight an Invisible Man?"

Thanks to Minutemen-PhD for these awesome digital copies. Please seed, and enjoy! :-)
